<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HR One - Inscription RH</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('styles.css') }}">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="shell">
      <header class="topbar">
        <a class="brand" href="{{ path('homepage') }}">
          <div class="brand-logo">
            <img src="{{ asset('navbarRH/logo.png') }}" alt="HR One">
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="brand-name">HR One</p>
            <p class="brand-sub">HR administrator onboarding</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <div class="nav-actions">
          <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('login') }}">Retour connexion</a>
          <a class="nav-cta" href="{{ path('signup_candidat') }}">Version candidat</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="layout">
        <section class="hero">
          <div class="hero-inner">
            <span class="eyebrow">Workspace RH</span>
            <h1>Launch HR operations with <span class="hero-highlight">control.</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-copy">
              Le parcours RH melange image enterprise et clarte d'execution:
              informations personnelles, donnees entreprise et presentation serieuse.
            </p>
            <div class="metrics">
              <div class="metric">
                <strong>360 deg</strong>
                <span>Vision complete du compte RH et de l'entreprise.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <strong>2 blocs</strong>
                <span>Organisation claire entre profil RH et societe.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <strong>1 base</strong>
                <span>Simple a enrichir avec validations et etapes.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="proof-card">
              <div class="proof-top">
                <span class="proof-badge">HR Admin</span>
                <span class="proof-stat">Enterprise flow</span>
              </div>
              <p>"La page inspire davantage confiance parce qu'elle ressemble a un vrai produit B2B."</p>
              <span class="proof-author">Adaptation inspiree des codes visuels SaaS haut de gamme</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="form-side">
          <div class="form-shell">
            <div class="form-topbar">
              <span class="micro-pill">Compte RH et entreprise</span>
              <span class="mini-meta">Setup admin</span>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-head">
              <h2>Creer un compte RH.</h2>
              <p>Commencez par les informations du responsable RH, puis ajoutez les donnees de l'entreprise.</p>
            </div>

            {% for message in app.flashes('error') %}
              <div style="color:red; margin: 12px 0;">{{ message }}</div>
            {% endfor %}
            {% for message in app.flashes('success') %}
              <div style="color:green; margin: 12px 0;">{{ message }}</div>
            {% endfor %}

            {{ form_start(form, {'attr': {'class': 'auth-form grid-2'}}) }}
              <p class="section-title full">Informations RH</p>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Nom d'utilisateur</label>
                {{ form_widget(form.username, {'attr': {'placeholder': "Nom d'utilisateur"}}) }}
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Mot de passe</label>
                {{ form_widget(form.password, {'attr': {'placeholder': 'Mot de passe'}}) }}
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Email</label>
                {{ form_widget(form.email, {'attr': {'placeholder': 'email@entreprise.com'}}) }}
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Adresse</label>
                {{ form_widget(form.address, {'attr': {'placeholder': 'Adresse'}}) }}
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Telephone</label>
                {{ form_widget(form.phone, {'attr': {'placeholder': '06 00 00 00 00'}}) }}
              </div>
              <p class="section-title full">Informations entreprise</p>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Nom de l'entreprise</label>
                {{ form_widget(form.company_name, {'attr': {'placeholder': "Nom de l'entreprise"}}) }}
              </div>
              <div class="actions full">
                {{ form_widget(form.submit, {'attr': {'class': 'btn btn-primary'}}) }}
                <a class="btn btn-outline" href="{{ path('login') }}">Retour connexion</a>
              </div>
            {{ form_end(form) }}

            <div class="trust-row">
              <span class="trust-chip">B2B friendly</span>
              <span class="trust-chip">Onboarding RH</span>
              <span class="trust-chip">Future scalable</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>